        it('has not change since tests were created', function() {

            gaSysAppModule.addQuery('application.title', '=', 'Drink Management');
            gaSysAppModule.addAggregate('COUNT');
            gaSysAppModule.query();
            var expected = '11';
            var count = 0;
            if (gaSysAppModule.next()) {
                count = gaSysAppModule.getAggregate('COUNT');
            }
            expect(count).toBe(expected);
        });
    });
